<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_CAS_FaceBody_HairstyleColor" s="315394">
  <T n="name">0xF1F738AB<!--String: "Hairstyle & Color"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Hair_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:d0037e1145771852</T>
      <T n="text">0x11DCA766<!--String: "You can edit the style and color of the <b><font color='#199C2C'>hair</font></b> on your Sim’s head by selecting their head, and then their hair (or the Hair button in the menu)."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_HairstyleAndColor_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:430eec59d2f657a1</T>
      <T n="text">0x1667445F<!--String: "There are a lot of <b><font color='#199C2C'>hairstyles</font></b> to choose from! From curly tresses and intricate braids to sharp bangs and mohawks, you’re sure to find a style that suits your Sim.\n\nTo make it easier to find what you’re looking for, you can sort by <b><font color='#199C2C'>category</font></b> (Short, Medium, Long, and Updo) or use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>filters</font></b>. For example, you can filter by Texture to look for Afro-Textured, Straight, or Wavy styles!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_HairstyleAndColor_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:430eec59d2f657a0</T>
      <T n="text">0xA26B55C6<!--String: "You can have different hairstyles for different <b><font color='#199C2C'>Outfits</font></b>! Change your Outfit category with the Outfit buttons at the top of the Hairstyle Menu and then select a hairstyle in the menu below to set a style for that Outfit category."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_HairstyleAndColor_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:430eec59d2f657a7</T>
      <T n="text">0x7F6B620C<!--String: "<b><font color='#199C2C'>Hair color</font></b> is selected at the top of the Hairstyle menu. There are a lot of fun shades to choose from! Some even have dashing strands of gray in them.\n\nKeep in mind that your Sim will have the same hair color for every <b><font color='#199C2C'>Outfit</font></b> category."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
